            | .grid.no-grid-at-767
            |   .span4
            |   .span4
            |   .span4
        h4.bs-docs-heading Using both m-grid and no-grid
        p
          | You can use the mobile-grid for a range of breakpoints, and switch to the no-grid below a certain breakpoint. Simply add the appropriate
          code
            | .m-grid-at
          | &nbsp;and&nbsp;
          code
            | .no-grid-at
          | &nbsp;classes for the target breakpoints.
        p.p4
          | Resize your browser to below 768px wide, and then to below 568 wide, to see mobile-grid and no-grid each take effect at different breakpoints.
        div.grid.m-grid-at-767.no-grid-at-567.show-grid
          div.span4.m-span1
            | 4 m1
          div.span4.m-span2
