        h4.bs-docs-heading Full-bleed on small screens
        p
          | By default, margins are applied to small screens the same as desktop. The&nbsp;
          code
            | .full-bleed
          | &nbsp;(and&nbsp;
          code
            | .full-bleed-no-max
          | &nbsp;) classes will affect all resolution sizes. To apply full-bleed below 768px, when not used on desktop, use&nbsp;
          code
            | .full-bleed-at-767
          | ,&nbsp;
          code
            | .full-bleed-at-567
          | ,&nbsp;
          code
            | .full-bleed-at-479
          | , or&nbsp;
          code
            | .m-full-bleed
          | &nbsp;(same as&nbsp;
          code
            | .full-bleed-at-767
          | &nbsp;).
